  "reference_number": "RUS1757",
  "remarks": "\nLyubov KABAEVA is an involved person within the meaning of the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because she is the mother of Alina Kabaeva. Alina Kabaeva is Chair of National Media Group (NMG) and an involved person in destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine. Therefore, Lyubov KABAEVA is associated to an involved person. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
